  24:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                 ##### RIF main features #####
  25:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   ==============================================================================
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccsLeOrZ.s 			page 2


  26:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   [..]
  27:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (+) Resource Isolation framework (RIF) is a comprehensive set of hardware
  28:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     blocks designed to enforce and manage isolation of STM32 hardware resources
  29:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     like memory and peripherals.
  30:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  31:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (+) Resource Isolation Framework (RIF) composed of the following sub-blocks:
  32:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****       (++) RIMC:  Resource Isolation Master Controller
  33:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   This sub-block assigns all non RIF-aware bus master to one
  34:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   security domain by setting secure, privileged and compartment
  35:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   information on the system bus.
  36:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   Note that if non-secure software is permitted to configure one of
  37:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   these peripherals, then this setting is ignored and all accesses
  38:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   initiated by the peripheral are forced to be non-secure.
  39:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****       (++) RISC:  Resource Isolation Slave Controller
  40:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   This sub-block assigns all non-RIF aware peripherals to zero,
  41:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   one or any security domains (secure, privilege, compartment).
  42:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****       (++) RISAF: Resource Isolation Slave unit for Address space (Full version)
  43:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   This sub-block assigns memory regions and subregions to one or
  44:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   more security domains (secure, privilege, compartment).
  45:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****       (++) IAC:   Illegal Access Controller
  46:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   This sub-block centralizes detection of RIF-related accesses,
  47:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   managed by a secure application. Supported illegal accesses are:
  48:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                   secure, privileged.
  49:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  50:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   [..]
  51:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (+) All the setter functions are protected under the CPU_AS_TRUSTED_DOMAIN
  52:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         directive.
  53:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         It ensures that only the trusted domain can manage the critical
  54:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         configurations of the RIF.
  55:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         This directive is defined in the CMSIS file.
  56:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  57:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****  ===============================================================================
  58:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****                      ##### How to use this driver #####
  59:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****  ===============================================================================
  60:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   [..]
  61:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     *** Locking RIF components configuration ***
  62:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     ============================================================
  63:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     [..]
  64:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get the lock configuration of RIMC registers until next reset
  65:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         with HAL_RIF_RIMC_Lock / HAL_RIF_RIMC_GetLock.
  66:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get the lock configuration of RISC registers until next reset
  67:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         with HAL_RIF_RISC_Lock / HAL_RIF_RISC_GetLock.
  68:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get the lock configuration of slave resources registers until
  69:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         next reset with HAL_RIF_RISC_SlaveConfigLock / HAL_RIF_RISC_GetSlaveConfigLock.
  70:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get the lock configuration of RISAF registers until next reset
  71:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         with HAL_RIF_RISAF_Lock / HAL_RIF_RISAF_GetLock.
  72:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  73:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     *** Context-related functions ***
  74:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     ============================================================
  75:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     [..]
  76:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Set or get Debugger Access Port Compartment ID with HAL_RIF_RIMC_SetDebugAccessPortCID /
  77:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RIMC_GetDebugAccessPortCID functions.
  78:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Check the Debug Domain and Global Debug Domain status with
  79:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RIMC_GetDebugStatus.
  80:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  81:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** #if defined(GENERATOR_RIF_FEATURE_ENCRYPTION_IMPLEMENTED)
  82:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     *** Encryption-related functions ***
