  85:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Read of write RISAF encryption keys and related flags.
  86:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
