  88:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****      *** Configuration of master-related attributes ***
  89:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     ============================================================
  90:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     [..]
  91:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Set or get the secure, privilege and compartment configuration of a
  92:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         bus master thanks to the HAL_RIF_RIMC_ConfigMasterAttributes /
  93:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RIMC_GetConfigMasterAttributes functions.
  94:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get lock status the bus master attributes configuration until
  95:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         next system reset using HAL_RIF_RIMC_Lock.
  96:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
  97:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****      *** Configuration of slave-related attributes ***
  98:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     ============================================================
  99:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     [..]
 100:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Set or get the secure and privilege configuration of a bus slave
 101:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         thanks to the HAL_RIF_RISC_SetSlaveSecureAttributes /
 102:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RISC_GetSlaveSecureAttributes functions.
 103:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Lock and get lock status each bus slave attributes configuration using
 104:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RISC_SlaveConfigLock or lock the whole RISC configuration with
 105:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_RISC_Lock until next system reset.
 106:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c **** 
 107:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****      *** Configuration of RISAF attributes ***
