 121:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Enable or disable peripheral illegal access detection with HAL_RIF_IAC_EnableIT /
 122:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_IAC_DisableIT.
 123:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Retrieve an illegal access flag from a designated peripheral with HAL_RIF_IAC_GetFlag
 124:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         or clear it with HAL_RIF_IAC_ClearFlag.
 125:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Illegal access interrupt service routines are served by HAL_RIF_IRQHandler()
