1002:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   * @note   This API is protected by the Trusted Domain compilation directive.
1003:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   * @note   This API is protected by the TrustZone Enabled compilation directive.
1004:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   * @param  PeriphId specifies the index of the bus slave.
1005:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****   *         This parameter can be one of @ref RIF_PERIPHERAL_INDEX
